1
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:14,439
Why don't you run away?

2
00:00:16,719 --> 00:00:17,879
Look at these mountains.

3
00:00:18,640 --> 00:00:21,399
In my condition, I'd never make it out.

4
00:00:22,519 --> 00:00:23,800
These mountains aren't hard to cross.

5
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:24,879
I walk them every day.

6
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,679
That's just you.

7
00:00:28,879 --> 00:00:31,320
Besides, there are things

8
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:34,320
you wouldn't understand even if I told you.

9
00:00:35,079 --> 00:00:35,560
Little Stone.

10
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:38,159
If I ever manage to escape,

11
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:39,399
I'll definitely take you with me.

12
00:00:39,399 --> 00:00:41,560
I'll find a way to get you out of here.

13
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,679
Thank you, Little Stone.

14
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,560
You have to be careful too.

15
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,759
They're very dangerous.

16
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:53,920
Mm.

17
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:15,159
Wait for me over there.

18
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,040
Master Ren.

19
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:21,480
This is freshly harvested Maojian tea.

20
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:23,120
I brought it especially for you.

21
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:29,560
Ren Fanghai.

22
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,959
A wise man knows when to bend.

23
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:35,640
Surely you understand such a simple truth?

24
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,920
I know these years haven't been easy for you.

25
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,120
But as long as one is alive,

26
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:51,239
one has to have something to hope for, right?

27
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,319
Think about Ren Ran, too.

28
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,400
It's been four years.

29
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,879
It's only out of respect for you

30
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:05,200
that I've kept her from suffering too much.

31
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:07,879
You bastard.

32
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:16,159
This prescription.

33
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,800
Prepare it for me today,

34
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:19,080
and you'll get to see Ren Ran.

35
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:25,599
You wrote Angelica dahurica as White atractylodes.

36
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,719
White atractylodes.

37
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:29,360
And Pinellia Rhizome as Arisaema erubescens.

38
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,280
Arisaema erubescens.

39
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,159
Not a single herb in a prescription can be wrong.

40
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,120
A tiny error can lead to a huge disaster.

41
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:39,319
One wrong herb costs a life.

42
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,080
Understood?

43
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:43,280
Yes, Dad. I won't make that mistake again.

44
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:47,120
Only Feifan would write a prescription like this.

45
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:51,080
But why would Feifan deliberately write it?

46
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:53,080
Could it be he knows I'm still alive,

47
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:55,560
and that Wang Wenhao would bring it to me?

48
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:59,120
What is it? Is there a problem with the prescription?

49
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:02,400
Who gave you this prescription?

50
00:03:03,639 --> 00:03:05,240
That's none of your concern.

51
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:06,199
Just tell me,

52
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:08,319
is there anything wrong with this prescription?

53
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:10,639
Angelica dahurica is warm in nature,

54
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,120
mainly enters the lung, spleen, and stomach meridians.

55
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:16,680
It clashes with the cold herbs in this prescription.

56
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,719
This prescription is far too bold.

57
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,080
It might cure rare diseases and countless toxins,

58
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,960
but the dosage is too aggressive.

59
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,919
Look at this nux vomica.

60
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,159
This is absurd.

61
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:31,159
And such heavy doses of Aconite and Kusnezoff Monkshood.

62
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:31,919
This...

63
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,599
The consequences are unpredictable.

64
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:39,199
Treatment must prioritize the patient's safety.

65
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:41,000
You can't use such extreme measures.

66
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,759
If something goes wrong, then...

67
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,199
It seems what Ren Feifan said

68
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,159
wasn't entirely a lie.

69
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:54,280
That's not for you to worry about.

70
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,599
Just prepare this prescription for me.

71
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,639
Well?

72
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:02,400
If I'm right,

73
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:06,039
then this is Feifan trying to reach me.

74
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,120
I have to seize this chance,

75
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,960
starting with this prescription.

76
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:14,039
I'll take the risk and try.

77
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:15,680
Master Ren.

78
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,240
I'll watch you prepare the medicine.

79
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,920
You don't mind, do you?

80
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,639
You old fool!

81
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:41,439
What did you do?

82
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:46,160
I told you, adding Angelica dahurica to this

83
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,079
will trigger cold-heat antagonism

84
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,279
and produce toxins.

85
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,759
If you force this formula together,

86
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,879
the one preparing it gets poisoned first.

87
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:56,399
But once the remaining herbs are added,

88
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:58,600
the poison naturally dissipates.

89
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:02,079
Your dizziness just now was a sign of poisoning.

90
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:09,199
Master Ren, forgive my ignorance. Please continue.

91
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:20,199
What if Wang Wenhao makes Feifan test the drug?

92
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,160
What would happen then?

93
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,680
This

94
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,480
is poison.

95
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,959
Without the antidote within five minutes,

96
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,879
your guts will rupture and you'll die.

97
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:50,199
Wang Wenhao, you monster!

98
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,120
This next pill

99
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,839
was made from the formula you gave me.

100
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,000
Ren Feifan,

101
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:24,399
you'd better pray there's nothing wrong with it.

102
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,360
Otherwise,

103
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,480
your sister

104
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,720
and your father

105
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,920
will die alongside you.

106
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,800
Aren't you afraid of karma for wiping us all out?

107
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,120
I'll take the pill.

108
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:05,800
Let's go.

109
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:11,720
Brother.

110
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:13,720
That poison was real.

111
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,160
How could I ever give him the real formula?

112
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,600
I just gave myself an antidote shot beforehand.

113
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,360
To keep the poison from reaching my heart and lungs.

114
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:28,519
Wait...

115
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,319
Who are you calling?

116
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,720
Silly girl.

117
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,759
This medicine has the scent of Mist Spirit Herb.

118
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,160
It's the signal Father left for us.

119
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:41,680
Our family will be reunited very soon.

120
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,600
I need to ask you a favor.

121
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:51,560
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

122
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,720
Before I was certain,

123
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,160
I was afraid I'd tip them off.

124
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,480
Feifan, you know what?

125
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:03,040
Ever since that day, I've had nightmares.

126
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,360
In my dreams,

127
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:07,079
Uncle and Auntie Ren's eyes kept staring at me.

128
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,639
I couldn't bear to look at them.

129
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,839
For a while,

130
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:13,680
I thought I couldn't hold on anymore.

131
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,360
Until you got out of prison.

132
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:17,480
Only then did a flicker of hope return.

133
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:20,000
Now you tell me Uncle Ren is still alive.

134
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,480
Of course I'm coming with you.

135
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:24,360
But this trip will be extremely dangerous.

136
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,920
If you go alone and hide it from me,

137
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,560
I'll never forgive you as long as I live.

138
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,480
Feifan.

139
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,279
I won't hold you back.

140
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,840
I'm not the Xu Ruojin I was four years ago.

141
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:45,480
Let's go.

142
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:55,919
Feifan.

143
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:59,080
I don't know how this venture will end.

144
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,720
No matter what,

145
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,200
for your mother,

146
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,120
and to avenge the Ren family,

147
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,600
no matter the risk,

148
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,440
it's worth it.

149
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,720
The dew is heavy, the mist thick.

150
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:15,080
Feifan should have found the path by now.

151
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,000
Little Stone, where are you going?

152
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:23,559
Mr. Hero told me to come.

153
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,360
Mr. Hero?

154
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,600
What nonsense are you talking about?

155
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,679
There's this guy who looks like a real hero.

156
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,480
Mr. Hero.

157
00:09:32,799 --> 00:09:33,519
He told me,

158
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,360
if I could help get you off this mountain,

159
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,919
he'd take me away for a better life.

160
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:40,480
You've been acting strange all day.

161
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:42,000
Explain yourself clearly.

162
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,320
Besides, I've already told you,

163
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:47,360
in my condition, I can't get down this mountain.

164
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,960
I've got a plan.

165
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,159
Just do as I say.

166
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:52,120
Hey, not so fast.

167
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:57,000
Who is this hero you're talking about?

168
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,320
Why isn't he here himself?

169
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,759
I know the terrain, and I won't draw attention.

170
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:01,960
Come with me, quickly.

171
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,080
Those two guard dogs went down the mountain for women.

172
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:06,360
If we miss this chance, there won't be another.

173
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,080
I just overheard they're moving locations.

174
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,080
They leave tomorrow.

175
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,840
By then, no one can help you.

176
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:15,799
Oh, and the hero said

177
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:18,120
he's a very close friend of your son.

178
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:27,480
This wilderness... could Uncle Ren really be here?

179
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,200
My father must be somewhere on this mountain.

180
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,799
How can you be so sure?

181
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:37,080
My father used the formula to send me a code.

182
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:40,799
He said where Mist Spirit Herb grows, that's where he hides.

183
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:43,440
And within hundreds of miles,

184
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,120
this is the only place

185
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:50,320
where this herb grows.

186
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,799
Master, wake up.

187
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:25,279
Master, Master, wake up.

188
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,519
I must be out of my mind.

189
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,000
Following you, Little Stone,

190
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:33,960
this old life of mine

191
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,000
nearly ended right here.

192
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,039
Get up, quick.

193
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,360
Hurry, take a look.

194
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:44,759
Where the hell did we tumble to?

195
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:50,600
Damn, we're still in the mountains.

196
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,559
We didn't roll that far, did we?

197
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:55,720
Master, let me help you up first.

198
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,759
Kept me up the whole damn night,

199
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:05,559
searching all over the mountain for you.

200
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:07,759
Well, aren't you clever.

201
00:12:07,879 --> 00:12:08,960
Tied yourselves together.

202
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,399
Saves us the trouble.

203
00:12:24,759 --> 00:12:25,919
Feifan.

204
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,840
Feifan, I'm sorry.

205
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:35,679
Feifan, we're not going to make it back.

206
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:36,559
Are we?

207
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,480
Ruojin.

208
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:43,159
Actually...

209
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:46,360
Wake up.

210
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:52,840
You're awake.

211
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,480
Let's keep searching.

212
00:12:58,519 --> 00:12:59,240
Okay.
